<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Password</title>
    <style>
        * {
            font-family: sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 960px;
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }
        .header {
            padding: 1rem;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #cccccc;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 300px;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
        }
        .mt-1 {
            margin-top: .5rem;
        }
        .my-2 {
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .mb-2 {
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .text-center {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn {
            background: #0bae6b;
            color: #fafafa !important;
            display: inline-block;
            padding: .7rem 3rem;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            color: #898989;
            border-top: 1px solid #cccccc;
        }
        .footer_logo {
            max-width: 180px;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" class="logo"/>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Reset your password</h2>
            <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>Forgot your password?</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset the password for your account.</p>
            <p class="mb-2">To reset your password, click on the button below:</p>
            <div class="text-center mb-2">
                <a class="btn" href="{{resetUrl}}">Reset password</a>
            </div>
            <p>Please note that not all applications to join Proxy Manager are accepted. We will notify you of our decision by email within 24 hours.</p>
            <p>Thanks for your time</p>
            <p>The Proxy Manager Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <img src="{{logoUrl}}" class="footer_logo"/>
            <p class="mt-1">This email may contain confidential information intended solely for the recipient. If you have received this email in error, please notify the sender immediately and delete it from your system.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>